::Bloodystrike/Reptilica/Mosquitor/DeathScythe/Ramulus/DevilDuer/Perndabot::

DevilDuer, Bloodystrike and Reptilica each phaze in in their own quarters, 
each of them setting off for the bridge of the Alliance base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DeathScythe appears above the forest, resuming his flight toward the mountain 
range in front of him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus phazes back into reality, nearly crashing into a tree. He checks his 
scanners, seeing that DeathScythe has also returned. He continues his pursuit 
of the assassing, dodging trees as he gallops.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mosquitor looks around, walking toward the Predacon bridge. He enters, 
looking around for Black Arachnia. The bug needed orders, but Black Arachnia 
was nowhere to be seen. Mosquitor walks off down a hallway, looking for the 
spider.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Perndabot narrows his eyes, watching the entrance to the Cybertronian Fire 
carefully from his position. He had recieved BrightBlade's transmission, but 
no further word or action from her so far. He activates his comm-link, not 
taking his eyes off of the Maximal battle cruiser.

"Are you getting out of the main entrance?" he says into his comm, waiting 
for her to reply.
